There is no XBOX360 version of the game, what crap is this???!?
This is a moddified version of the XBOX version of the game to run on a 
XBOX360 console. I added a Security Sector, Stealth Files and used the original 
disc layout, to pad the disc to a DVD9.


Is it i-Xtreme compatible?
Yes, i tested it myself on an i-Xtreme 1.4 flashed drive.


Will this run on my XBOX360?
 There are 3 things you need to play this game!
 
 1.) The XBOX original games emulator from Microsoft. I recommend Nov2007 update.
 <a href=" http://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/backwardscompatibility.htm" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/backwardscompatibility.htm</a> 
  
 2.) A harddisc for your XBOX360, because the emulator from Microsoft needs it.

 3.) An i-Xtreme firmware flashed drive.
 


Why a DVD9?
Because some Hitachi drives and maybe some other drives with i-Xtreme Firmware have 
problems reading backups from a DVD-5!



Will i get banned?

BUT it is stealthed, like any other backup on the net. This gurantees at the moment

backup on the net, they will not detect this one. So enjoy!
